23/07/2009
PRISTINA, Kosovo -- Police arrested an unidentified person on Wednesday (July 22nd) who is suspected of planting two hand grenades in a conference room of the Pristina Municipal Assembly.
Police say the suspect has an ongoing property dispute with local authorities.
Police and KFOR recovered the grenades before they could explode.
(Lajm, Express, Koha Ditore, Zeri, Epoka e Re, Telegrafi - 23/07/09)
